# Web testing bar

Full reference: [docs/domain/web-testing.md](../../docs/domain/web-testing.md).

## Rules

1. **MSW only for new tests** — `server.use(handlers)` from `web/src/test/handlers/`. No new `vi.spyOn(globalThis, "fetch")`.
2. **No bare sleeps** — `vi.useFakeTimers()` or `createDeferred()`; never `setTimeout` or `new Promise(() => {})`.
3. **Project placement** — `unit` / `components` / `integration` per `web/vitest.workspace.ts`. `<App />` and pages belong in `integration`.
4. **≤ 500 lines** per `*.test.{ts,tsx}`.
5. **Keep tests fast** — prefer handlers + `renderHook` over full-app renders when the behaviour is local.

## Good

```ts
server.use(...appDefaultHandlers(), tasksListEmpty());
renderApp();
```

## Bad

```ts
vi.spyOn(globalThis, "fetch").mockImplementation(async (input) => { /* 40 lines */ });
```
